sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Ingress<br/>(Istio/Gateway API)<br/>TLS Termination
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>FastAPI/Uvicorn<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>grpcio<br/>8081/TCP
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Batcher as Adaptive Batcher<br/>(optional)
    participant Cache as Response Cache<br/>(optional)
    participant Model as MLModel.predict()<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lgbm/onnx)
    participant Worker as Parallel Worker<br/>(multiprocessing)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector
    participant Kafka as Kafka Brokers<br/>9092/TCP
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>/mnt/models

    Note over Client,KServe: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>KServe: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.3<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    KServe->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/8080 (plaintext, pod-internal)
    REST->>DP: Route request via FastAPI
    DP->>Cache: Check response cache (if enabled)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Batcher: Queue request (if adaptive batching enabled)
        Batcher->>Model: Batched predict() call
        Model-->>Batcher: Prediction result
        Batcher-->>DP: Individual response
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>KServe: HTTP 200 JSON response
    KServe-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,GRPC: Flow 2: gRPC Streaming Inference
    Client->>KServe: gRPC ModelStreamInfer<br/>HTTPS/443
    KServe->>GRPC: gRPC stream<br/>8081/TCP (plaintext)
    GRPC->>DP: Streaming inference request
    DP->>Model: predict_stream() async iterator
    loop Streaming responses
        Model-->>DP: Partial result
        DP-->>GRPC: Stream chunk
        GRPC-->>KServe: gRPC stream response
        KServe-->>Client: Stream chunk
    end

    Note over DP,Worker: Flow 3: Parallel Worker Inference
    DP->>Worker: Dispatch via multiprocessing.Queue<br/>(Pickle/IPC)
    Worker->>Model: predict() in worker process<br/>(separate GIL)
    Model-->>Worker: Prediction result
    Worker-->>DP: Response via Queue<br/>(Pickle/IPC)

    Note over Kafka,DP: Flow 4: Kafka Async Inference
    Kafka->>DP: Consume from input topic<br/>TCP/9092
    DP->>Model: infer()
    Model-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP->>Kafka: Produce to output topic<br/>TCP/9092

    Note over Prom,Metrics: Flow 5: Metrics & Tracing
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(request counts, latencies, batch queue)
    REST->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)
    GRPC->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)

    Note over Storage,Model: Flow 6: Model Loading
    REST->>DP: POST /v2/repository/models/{name}/load<br/>(from KServe Agent)
    DP->>Storage: Read model artifacts<br/>from /mnt/models (filesystem)
    Storage-->>DP: Model files
    DP->>Model: Initialize runtime & load model
